{"word":"G3825 - πάλιν - pálin - pal'-in - Again","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πάλιν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pálin"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pal'-in"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Again"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"மறுபடியும், மேலும், இன்னமும், அன்றியும் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"anew, again"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from the same as <a href=\"#/G3823 - πάλη - pálē - pal'-ay/3823\">G3823</a> (through the idea of <i>oscillatory</i> repetition); (adverbially) <i>anew</i>, that is, (of place) <i>back</i>, (of time) <i>once more</i>, or (conjugationally) <i>furthermore</i> or <i>on the other hand:</i> - again."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}